Record Pair has left: i32; right: i32.

To make pair from owned, giving Pair.
Let cells be owned buffer of 2 i32 filled with 0.
cells at 0 becomes 3.
cells at 1 becomes 4.
Give Pair with left be cells at 0 and right be cells at 1.

To main, giving i32.
Let pair be make pair from owned.
Give pair.left plus pair.right.
